hits.definition:
议 (F 議)

[yì] (= 议论 yìlùn) discuss, confer;

    会议 huìyì meeting, conference;

    建议 jiànyì suggest, propose

形

[xíng] (= 形式 xíngshì) form, shape;

    形成 xíngchéng to form, take shape

早

[zǎo] early;

    早饭 zǎofàn breakfast;

    早晨 zǎochen morning

音

[yīn] (= 声音 shēngyīn) sound;

    音乐 yīnyuè music

火

[huǒ] fire;

    火车 huǒchē train;

    火柴 huǒchái match;

    火焰 huǒyàn flame

际 (F 際)

[jì] (= 边际 biānjì) boundary;

    实际 shíjì reality;

    国际 guójì international

则 (F 則)

[zé] (conjunction);

    原则 yuánzé principle;

    否则 fǒuzé or else

首

[shǒu] head;

    首先 shǒuxiān first of all;

    首都 shǒudū capital (of a country)

导 (F 導)

[dǎo] lead;

    领导 lǐngdǎo leader

影

[yǐng] shadow, image;

    电影 diànyǐng movie

失

[shī] lose;

    失败 shībài be defeated

{Compare with 先 xiān first}

拿

[ná] hold;

    拿来 nálái bring;

    拿去 náqù take;

    拿给 nágěi hand over

网 (F 網)

[wǎng] net;

    网球 wǎngqiú tennis;

    因特网 yīntèwáng Internet

香

[xiāng] perfume, fragrant;

    香港 Xiānggǎng Hong Kong

斯

[sī] thus (nowadays used mostly as a phonem in foreign names);

    法西斯 fǎxīsī Fascist
